      • getAllTypeAnnotations

        public TypeAnnotationsReader.TypeAnnotationAttribute[] getAllTypeAnnotations()
                                                                      throws InvalidClassFileException
        Returns:
        an array TypeAnnotationAttribute[] corresponding to the annotations[num_annotations] table specified as: 
         RuntimeVisibleTypeAnnotations_attribute {
   u2              attribute_name_index;
   u4              attribute_length;
   u2              num_annotations;
   type_annotation annotations[num_annotations];
 }
        Throws:
        InvalidClassFileException
        See Also:
        JLS (SE8), 4.7.20
